         <abstract id="aspace_1091257a9355d4c46f12877b84ddba2d">The records consist of minutes, reports, and memoranda documenting the activities and operations of the Yale College Board of Permanent Officers. Also included are materials on faculty appointments for Yale College and the graduate schools.</abstract>
