      <odd id="aspace_1d94ad1b4b3fbc179ecf8cd20966660a">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 9-C (YRG 9-C), Records of Yale College officers and faculty.</p>  
      </odd>
      <altformavail id="aspace_1600acee23de80c7689cab68e56465ad">
         <head>Existence and Location of Copies</head>
         <p>Minutes of meetings (1871-1956) are available on microfilm (442 frames on 1 reel, 35mm) from Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library, at cost. Order no. HM216.</p>  
      </altformavail>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_46bbfaa18c9ddecda94c03a972a1c007">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>While this collection as a whole is available for research, parts of it may be restricted due to law, university policy or fragility. Any restricted material will be noted as such. See Collection Contents for details.</p>
         <p>Minutes of meetings (1871-1956) are available on microfilm. Patrons must use HM 216 instead of the originals.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_1719847df828386511b13f54ba8cd7ce">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Board of Permanent Officers, Yale College, Records (RU 542). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_b37ee5a614fdd335e9d22912dc8a9b6f">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_182d1bc94ea7621825a324843e7d0180">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of minutes, reports, and memoranda documenting the activities and operations of the Yale College Board of Permanent Officers. Also included are materials on faculty appointments for Yale College and the graduate schools.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
